{"tid":1846454,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"陳雲：不封關是禍害香港的政策","createTime":"2020-01-27T15:31:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T06:26:34.000Z","uid":210140,"like":15,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e735298d8f2700c46df00c7d6036e0870011f7cc","tid":1846454,"uid":210140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T15:31:19.000Z","msg":"陳雲：政府不封關而給予確診武漢肺炎的外地人免費醫療，只會吸引大陸人過關來港就醫。給予確診者免費就醫是合理的，但不封關的話，這個政策有以下弊端：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一、Attraction effect. 吸引大陸人來港就醫。由於武漢肺炎的高燒不一定明顯，通過體溫測試而來港是容易的，變成逼爆想香港醫院。<br />\n<br />\n二、Crowding out effect. 增加醫院感染，令本地人不敢去公立醫院，產生排擠效應（crowding out），增加其他疾病的死亡率。如果轉去私人診所或醫院求醫，也會逼爆。<br />\n<br />\n三、Overburdening. 武漢肺炎這類並無特效藥及只能用長期舒緩性質的治療，會佔據香港病床，令香港醫療開支沉重。</span></strong></span><br />\n毫無疑問，這是禍害香港的政策。<br />\n（按：我建議的封關是比較溫和的，是禁止自由行之類的大陸客，商務、公務及探親仍可檢疫之後入境。）<br />\n附加未經證實的消息：來自連登討論區的消息傳出，//（國家）衛健委認為香港目前依然擁有中國境內最完善的醫療制度，以及在03年SARS疫情中累積的豐富傳染病處理經驗。建議可利用香港，疏導一部份國內患者前往香港接受隔離治療，以協助內地控制肺炎患者的流動降低傳播風險。否則以目前大陸的情況，大量遊離患者將在得不到隔離照顧的情況下，四處遊走加劇疫情傳播。<br />\n林鄭在接獲中央政府要求後，隨即向行會成員及下轄管治班子聲明將拒絕任何封關的可能性，並於27日透過衛生署正式公佈：「內地肺炎患者將於香港獲得免費醫療」的措施，以配合中央疏導病患至香港加以控制隔離的疫管措施。若消息屬實，香港或將成為這次肺炎疫情中最無辜的犧牲者。//"},{"pid":"9caeaa64b4eed93fe4ec9844873e2faab0bf02cf","tid":1846454,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T15:32:18.000Z","msg":"竟然有食藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7257949a12d09271f753b19901e5575b17260ba","tid":1846454,"uid":210140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9caeaa64b4eed93fe4ec9844873e2faab0bf02cf","tid":1846454,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T15:32:18.000Z","msg":"竟然有食藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T15:32:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望林鄭既呢位老同事可以睇下佢講左乜"},{"pid":"54c4bdc3162b0ccd29a40f576d66cc7502c37fc7","tid":1846454,"uid":185045,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T15:36:23.000Z","msg":"連平日唔食藥的講野都可以咁正常<br />\n你就知道個政府有幾垃圾"},{"pid":"bc2def8f65640ab6505ad2f83a5a3f55ffa40e8d","tid":1846454,"uid":98993,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T15:37:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"05b3b53b4e3159e88085b7fb407ae0c506f72307","tid":1846454,"uid":103230,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T15:37:28.000Z","msg":"壞既鐘一日會準兩次"},{"pid":"3e3a7ee6654d995de37a13b7968d29bef0d7011c","tid":1846454,"uid":117009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T15:37:57.000Z","msg":"又話只係勁啲嘅流感唔需要防嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36939b6ebf95bd3bf548e41ddd4502830734a013","tid":1846454,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T15:38:15.000Z","msg":"Objective:<br />\n&gt; Shut down the airline from HK, if Carrie Lam fails to block the border.<br />\n&gt; Given Fact: Japan and Macau found #WuhanSARS patients who are from #HKG Airport =&gt; No checking in the departure. <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rHg8fGB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrHg8fGB.png&h=077d795f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSolomon都有講話禁止中國航班飛美國，不過要請佢留意埋香港：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SolomonYue/status/1221454591335653377\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue%2F